msgid "National land cover legends and regional transition matrices may be more accurate in capturing local degradation processes and land cover transitions, but might increase the number of possible land cover transitions to be described to an unmanageable amount. While it is important to include the key land cover transitions in a country, a balance between precision and manageability of the information should be considered."
