#: ../../SO1.md:510
msgid "Existing national land cover maps and data need to be converted to the seven UNCCD classes. The required aggregation of land cover classes to the seven UNCCD classes can partly degrade the quality of the original data. Documenting the uncertainties and generalizations applied to harmonize data with international standards may inform the conversion process and the accuracy of the outputs."
