msgid "An in-depth reading of Section 1 and Section 3 of the [Addendum to Good Practice Guidance for SDG Indicator 15.3.1](https://www.unccd.int/resources/manuals-and-guides/addendum-good-practice-guidance-sdg-indicator-1531-proportion-land): Proportion of land that is degraded over total land area (version 2), which details a number of methodological approaches to calculating land productivity changes;"
