#: ../../SO1.md:1013
msgid "1.3.3. Reporting process and step-by-step procedure"
msgstr ""

#: ../../SO1.md:1015
msgid "For the 2026 national reporting process, the following information for SO1-3 is needed:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../SO1.md:1017
