msgid "Step 5. Save form and make available for review"
msgstr ""

#: ../../SO1.md:1436
msgid "Special or anomalous situations and noticeable issues related to the data interpretation that may affect the reliability of the reported values should be described in the narrative. A ‘General Comments’ field is provided at the end of the reporting form of the PRAIS 4 platform for this purpose."
msgstr ""

#: ../../SO1.md:1439
msgid "Information on land degradation should be reported in km2 for the entire country."
msgstr ""

